     H            Y.
     F*** T#MR01 ***************************************************************
     F*  PROGRAM    : SET 1 TO BOX COUNT(8) OF AGAPP31                         *
     F*  WRITTEN    : 06/01/2016                                               *
     F*  WRITTEN BY : JW (SRA)                                                 *
     F*------------------------------------------------------------------------*
     F*  ** ATTENTION **                                                       *
     F*  ** COMPILE WITH ALLOW NULL *YES
     F**************************************************************************
     FLEVEL   IF  E                    DISK
     FAGAPL31 UF  E           K        DISK
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  14 K@PART
     I                                        1   5 K@SHN1
     I                                        6   6 HI1
     I                                        7  11 K@SHN2
     I                                       12  12 HI2
     I                                       13  14 K@SHN3
      *
     I           SDS
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
     I                                      264 269 #JBNO
     F**************************************************************************
     C                     EXSR #INIT
      *
     C           *IN98     DOWEQ*OFF
     C                     READ LEVEL                    98
     C           *IN98     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     MOVELL1PART    K@PART
     C           KEY       CHAINAGAPL31              99
     C           *IN99     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     Z-ADD1         CBHK08
     C                     UPDATAGAPL311
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *  INITIAL SETTING                                   *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     C           #INIT     BEGSR
      *
     C           KEY       KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K@SHN1
     C                     KFLD           K@SHN2
     C                     KFLD           K@SHN3
      *
     C           XINIT     ENDSR
